                        "en": {"text": "<p>I am a reflective problem-solver who enjoys using <b>programming</b> to develop systems that enhance efficiency and convenience. I prioritize user needs and incorporate <b>UX design</b> to facilitate clear and effective communication. By integrating these skills, I create systems that not only meet requirements but also provide meaningful solutions to real-world challenge.</p>"},
